Bolivar Street, north side, west from Navy Street in the foreground, to Hudson Ave., in the background. Also seen is 192-196 Navy Street, at the N.W. corner of Bolivar Street. On Hudson Ave., is also seen the Fifth Ave., Elevated Lines of the B.M.T.
